      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "my brethren, these things ought not so to be: in any, and much less in professors of religion: such things are unbecoming men, are a scandal upon human nature, and exceeding unworthy of the Christian name; see Psalm 50:16. ",
        "children": [
          {
